Amazon MX Player mempersembahkan
Aukaat Ke Bahar - Trailer Resmi

Dibintangi: Elvish Yadav, Malhaar Rathod, Nikhil Vijay, Hetal Gada, Rohan Khurrana, Keshav Sadhna

Dikembangkan, Cerita, Skenario, dan Ditulis oleh: Jayati Pandya, Akhilesh Vats, Jasmeet Bhatia, Ayush Gaur, Sumbul Khan, Siddharth Saini

Genre: Drama Romantis

Tentang Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, seorang petinju kota kecil dari Safidon, memasuki perguruan tinggi elit St. Collins di Delhi untuk mewujudkan impian saudaranya menjadi lulusan yang cerdas dan berbahasa Inggris. Di tengah perundungan, kejutan budaya, dan perbedaan kelas, ia jatuh cinta pada Antara Shukla ‚Äî seorang mahasiswa tingkat akhir dengan aspirasi politik yang jauh di luar kemampuannya. Ketika sebuah tantangan yang memalukan berbenturan dengan perasaannya yang semakin kuat dan krisis keluarga di kampung halaman, Rajveer harus berjuang lebih keras dari sebelumnya ‚Äî kali ini, bukan demi kejayaan, melainkan demi cinta, martabat, dan kelangsungan hidup.

Tentang Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player adalah layanan hiburan gratis, premium, dan beriklan terkemuka di India. Layanan ini menawarkan beragam serial web pemenang penghargaan, acara realitas, acara internasional populer, dan koleksi film yang sangat banyak dari berbagai genre. Dengan fokus yang kuat pada konten orisinal, Amazon MX Player telah meluncurkan beberapa acara terbesar di India, termasuk Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, Who‚Äôs your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter ‚Äì Totega Nahi Todega, dan banyak lagi. Amazon MX Player juga menawarkan beragam pilihan konten internasional yang dialihbahasakan ke dalam bahasa Hindi, Tamil, dan Telugu di bawah naungan MX Vdesi, menampilkan acara-acara populer seperti What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, dan banyak lagi!

snippet.title: Stranger Things - Season 5 Volume 2 Teaser Trailer | NETFLIX | 25 December, 2025
snippet.description:
#netflix #strangerthings5 #strangerthings 

Watch the 'FAN (CONCEPT) Trailer Concept' For Stranger Things - Season 5 (2025) (More Info About This Video Down Below!)

‚ñ∂Ô∏è Watch More Concept Trailers:

Harry Potter and the Cursed Child Trailer - https://youtu.be/OnwogtoNJSA üëà

Frozen: Live Action Movie Trailer -  https://youtu.be/5FlLO5EpNic üëà

Pirates of the Caribbean 6 Trailer - https://youtu.be/uncc9uN0bbIüëà

Get ready for the epic conclusion of Netflix's beloved sci-fi horror series with the Stranger Things Season 5 trailer. Set to premiere in November 2025, this final season promises to deliver a thrilling culmination to the Hawkins saga. After delays caused by industry strikes, production wrapped in December 2024, and post-production is ahead of schedule . The Duffer Brothers have crafted an ambitious season described as "eight blockbuster movies," focusing on emotional depth and high-stakes action .

The narrative centers on the Hawkins crew's ultimate battle against Vecna, delving deeper into the mysteries of the Upside Down. snippet.description:
#Revibe invites you to immerse yourself in the timeless classic "#KehnaHiKya" by the mellifluous #Chitra, featured in the iconic movie "#Bombay." This musical gem is a journey into the heart of melody and emotion, a song that transcends the boundaries of time and language, leaving an indelible mark on the soul.

Chitra's enchanting vocals in "Kehna Hi Kya" effortlessly convey the depths of love and longing, creating a musical experience that resonates with every listener. With its poetic lyrics and evocative composition, this song has become an anthem of romance and a testament to the power of music to touch the heart.

Credits: 
Singer: Chitra
Music: A. R. Rahman
Lyrics: Mehboob
Movie: Bombay
Starring: Arvind Swamy, Manisha Koirala

Producer: S.Sriram
Label: Universal Music India

snippet.description:
i have to escape before i am executed

Escaping Prison on the Unstable SMP / Escaping LAW: Minecraft's Largest Empire

minor spoilers below

featuring: @Spokeishere @PrinceZam @Fantst @Baablu  @loppezz @LettuceK @Lomedy 

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of the music I use is by AZALI so check him out!) (actually I don't think I used any AZALI in this video LOL)
https://www.youtube.com/@andreaszoeller (aria math remix)
https://www.youtube.com/@DMDOKURO (i believe the track that i used is just called void) 

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe / Unstable SMP that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, official enderal soundtrack, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

Enderal Soundtrack (HQ): Bone Hunter - Knochenj√§ger https://youtu.be/LchGhXSXxZk by Marvin Kopp, licensed under CC BY 4.0 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

snippet.title: Men's War Games Part 2 | WWE Survivor Series War Games - 11/29/2025
snippet.description:
WWE Survivor Series 2025 Men's WarGames: CM Punk, Cody Rhodes, Roman Reigns & Usos DESTROY Lesnar's squad! Epic chaos in San Diego! üî•
Relive the BRUTAL WarGames showdown from Survivor Series 2025 at Petco Park‚Äîwhere Undisputed WWE Champion Cody Rhodes teamed with World Heavyweight Champion CM Punk, The Tribal Chief Roman Reigns, and The Usos (Jey Uso & Jimmy Uso) to clash against a monstrous heel alliance: Brock Lesnar, Drew McIntyre, Logan Paul, and The Vision's Bron Breakker & Bronson Reed! This star-studded cage massacre featured non-stop spears, F-5s, Cross Rhodes, GTS finishers, Claymore Kicks, and tsunami splashes that left the stadium in shock. With Paul Heyman scheming from ringside and generational beefs exploding (Reigns vs. Lesnar rematch vibes, Punk's fire vs. McIntyre's rage, Usos' family unity vs. Paul's antics), this match redefined WarGames brutality and set the stage for WrestleMania 42 chaos. Who survived the double-cage inferno? Full highlights, key moments, and post-match fallout‚Äîdon't miss the highlights that broke the internet!
Did your favorite team pull off the W, or was it pure anarchy? Drop your MVP pick in the comments below! üëá

snippet.title: Meri Kismat Mein Tu Nahin Shayad Lyrical | Lata Mangeshkar | Suresh Wadkar | Prem Rog | Rishi Kapoor
snippet.description:
